WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.470
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.950
Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:07.269
Well, it's Brandon and Diana again,

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:09.110
and we have some things on our heart.

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:11.030
You know, I've been asking the Lord,

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:13.190
'Lord, there's a lot going on

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.230
right now. There is a lot going

00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:16.240
on.'I

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.230
told you all we would start to see these

00:00:18.230 --> 00:00:18.240
things—what

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:19.750
the spirit of the Lord was

00:00:19.760 --> 00:00:21.910
showing me in prayer:

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:25.070
the earthquakes, the

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:28.230
wars and rumors of wars, the

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:32.870
escalation with Iran. It seems

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:36.229
like all is being stirred up like a

00:00:36.239 --> 00:00:39.430
pot, isn't it? But you can feel there's

00:00:39.440 --> 00:00:41.430
something major about to take

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:43.510
place. And then we have all the

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:46.310
tariffs happening and all the things

00:00:46.320 --> 00:00:48.069
going on with that, and the economy

00:00:48.079 --> 00:00:49.910
crashing 1,500 points the day before and

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:54.790
2,000 today, and most people are like,

00:00:54.800 --> 00:00:57.430
'What's going on?'You know, and

00:00:57.440 --> 00:00:58.709
everybody wants to—'Where'd you go,

00:00:58.709 --> 00:00:58.719
Braden?'Listen,

00:00:58.719 --> 00:01:01.349
if I don't feel the

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:04.229
presence of the Lord on a video and I

00:01:04.239 --> 00:01:06.789
watch it back with my family and I

00:01:06.799 --> 00:01:09.429
just go, 'I'm not going to

00:01:09.439 --> 00:01:11.670
release it.'I vowed to

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:15.190
the Lord: if I do not sense the presence

00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:17.990
of the Lord on a video, I'm doing my

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.429
best. You know, some of them you may

00:01:19.439 --> 00:01:20.550
say, 'Well, I didn't feel nothing on

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:22.950
that video.'Well, it was

00:01:22.950 --> 00:01:22.960
semi-okay,

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:26.230
so I release it. But I'm

00:01:26.240 --> 00:01:28.870
telling you, if I feel a video is dry,

00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:30.550
I'm not going to waste

00:01:30.550 --> 00:01:30.560
your

00:01:30.560 --> 00:01:33.190
time. I just don't want to waste

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:35.109
your time. I'd rather it just be

00:01:35.119 --> 00:01:37.270
nothing on the air at all than for me

00:01:37.270 --> 00:01:37.280
to

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:40.469
come on here and just ramble around.

00:01:40.479 --> 00:01:42.950
If I feel a leading, I'm going to put it

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:45.230
out, and this is one I feel a leading

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:48.469
on. I was praying and I was asking the

00:01:48.479 --> 00:01:52.149
Lord about things, and He said, 'I

00:01:52.159 --> 00:01:54.190
want you to start reading the book of

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:56.789
Jeremiah. I want you to go over

00:01:56.799 --> 00:01:58.950
Jeremiah and look at what

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:00.870
he went through and the things that I

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:03.670
called him to say and warn the people

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:05.590
that were not ready to hear what he had

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:08.150
to say.'They persecuted him for what

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:10.630
was coming. They persecuted him because

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:12.390
of the things that he was saying and

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:15.030
decreeing by the

00:02:15.040 --> 00:02:18.390
voice of the Lord. He was saying, 'Hey,

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:20.229
this judgment's coming. These things are

00:02:20.229 --> 00:02:20.239
coming.'And

00:02:20.239 --> 00:02:22.710
you have a lot of

00:02:22.710 --> 00:02:22.720
itching-ear

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:26.309
people right now, a lot of

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:29.510
prophetic voices like I told you all

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:33.550
that are giving words at a level down

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:36.229
here. I'm not here

00:02:36.239 --> 00:02:38.070
to criticize because I'm not going to point

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:40.550
any names out; I'm

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:41.750
just telling you what I've heard the

00:02:41.760 --> 00:02:43.309
spirit of the Lord

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:45.869
say. They're

00:02:45.879 --> 00:02:49.670
so apt to want to be the first is what

00:02:49.680 --> 00:02:53.830
I'm hearing—to be the one that is

00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:56.869
always in the spotlight like a Hollywood

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:59.949
celebrity wanting to have their name in

00:02:59.959 --> 00:03:04.470
lights instead of going higher. And the

00:03:04.480 --> 00:03:06.390
Lord told me, 'There's a lot of

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:08.790
my ministers that are speaking from a

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:11.830
level down here instead of looking out

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:14.309
like an eagle. They're not looking at

00:03:14.319 --> 00:03:16.710
the eagle level. They're prophesying

00:03:16.720 --> 00:03:19.509
down here with the

00:03:19.509 --> 00:03:19.519
chickens.'And

00:03:19.519 --> 00:03:21.750
He said, 'And when you do that,

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.830
you're only able to see the trees in

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:27.030
front of your face. You cannot see from

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:31.509
a far distance what's coming

00:03:31.519 --> 00:03:33.910
to warn the people because you're

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:36.630
prophesying down where the chickens are.

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:38.869
And if you don't get up where the eagles

00:03:38.879 --> 00:03:41.190
are because the eagle has an eagle-eyed

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:44.229
view and they're able to see

00:03:44.239 --> 00:03:46.789
miles away.'An

00:03:46.789 --> 00:03:46.799
eagle is

00:03:46.799 --> 00:03:48.789
able to see miles; they're able

00:03:48.799 --> 00:03:51.190
to see a long way and they're able to

00:03:51.200 --> 00:03:54.229
tell what's coming in the

00:03:54.239 --> 00:03:56.229
future from storms or whatever because

00:03:56.239 --> 00:03:58.470
they're able to see it. But if

00:03:58.480 --> 00:03:59.670
they're down there with the chickens,

00:03:59.680 --> 00:04:01.910
you're only able to see the trees. So, you're

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:04.070
prophesying at the tree level and you

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.710
need to come up higher in the mountain

00:04:05.720 --> 00:04:09.429
level. And that's where the Lord is. And

00:04:09.439 --> 00:04:10.990
the Lord told me,

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:15.429
'Brandon, are you not in the end times

00:04:15.439 --> 00:04:18.069
right

00:04:18.069 --> 00:04:18.079
now?'I

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:20.310
said, 'Well, we see the signs,

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:22.950
Lord. Of course I believe we're

00:04:22.960 --> 00:04:24.390
in the end times.'And He said,

00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:27.350
'Then what did I say in my word was

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:32.469
coming for those end-time people? If

00:04:32.479 --> 00:04:35.469
your generation is the closer

00:04:35.469 --> 00:04:35.479
generation—and

00:04:35.479 --> 00:04:37.350
we've heard it and

00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:38.550
heard

00:04:38.550 --> 00:04:38.560
it—if

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:40.950
you

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:42.870
are a closer generation, what are you

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:44.870
expecting to come?'And He gave me

00:04:44.880 --> 00:04:46.189
Matthew

00:04:46.199 --> 00:04:49.590
24. I want

00:04:49.600 --> 00:04:54.110
Diana to read

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:57.749
this. And this is not a feel-good

00:04:57.759 --> 00:04:59.909
passage. This is not a feel-good, 'Wow,

00:04:59.919 --> 00:05:01.749
this makes me feel good. Oh, good times

00:05:01.759 --> 00:05:04.070
are coming.'If we're living in the

00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:06.870
last days, if we truly are living in the

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:10.029
last days, what are we supposed to

00:05:10.039 --> 00:05:13.029
expect with an eagle-eyed view? What

00:05:13.039 --> 00:05:15.350
are we looking for? So,

00:05:15.360 --> 00:05:17.029
are we looking like everybody's saying

00:05:17.039 --> 00:05:18.870
there's good days coming, all this

00:05:18.880 --> 00:05:21.629
greatness is coming, 'Boy, I tell you

00:05:21.639 --> 00:05:24.150
what, this is going to be the best of

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:25.909
the best'?

00:05:25.919 --> 00:05:29.270
Are we off when we say that? I don't

00:05:29.280 --> 00:05:31.189
know. Let's see. We're in the end times,

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:32.790
right? So, what is the end? What did

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:36.870
Jesus say we're supposed to expect? Go

00:05:36.880 --> 00:05:39.830
ahead and read chapter 24, verse 4. I want

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:42.150
you to start there.

00:05:42.160 --> 00:05:45.110
Jesus answered them, 'Be careful

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:47.909
that no one mislead you, deceiving you

00:05:47.919 --> 00:05:50.870
and leading you into error. For

00:05:50.880 --> 00:05:53.270
many will come in on the strength of my

00:05:53.280 --> 00:05:55.189
name, appropriating the name which

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:57.590
belongs to me, saying, "I am the Christ,

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:59.390
the Messiah,"and they will lead many

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:01.909
astray. And you will hear of wars and

00:06:01.919 --> 00:06:04.150
rumors of wars. See that you are not

00:06:12.400 --> 00:06:15.510
frightened or troubled,

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:18.309
for this must take place, but the end is

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:21.670
not yet. For nation will rise against

00:06:21.680 --> 00:06:25.110
nation, and kingdom against kingdom, and

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:27.830
there will be famines and earthquakes in

00:06:27.840 --> 00:06:31.150
place after place.'Pause. There'll be

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:33.230
famines and there's going to be

00:06:33.240 --> 00:06:35.510
earthquakes in place after place. So,

00:06:35.520 --> 00:06:36.790
there's going to be

00:06:36.800 --> 00:06:38.550
earthquakes all over the place, major

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:40.309
earthquakes. What I tell you is

00:06:40.309 --> 00:06:40.319
coming—the

00:06:40.319 --> 00:06:43.110
Lord said in 2025 we're going to

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:45.270
start to see major earthquakes. Then we

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:47.590
had the one in Asia. Then

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:50.150
we had another one in Asia. There's more

00:06:50.160 --> 00:06:53.270
coming. Keep going. There's

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:56.710
pestilence and earthquakes,

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:59.909
wars, rumors of wars. Keep going. 'All

00:06:59.919 --> 00:07:03.110
this is the beginning, the early pains

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:05.390
of the birth pains of

00:07:05.400 --> 00:07:08.790
intolerable anguish. They will hand you

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:10.749
over to suffer affliction and

00:07:10.759 --> 00:07:13.510
tribulation and put you to death. And

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:15.830
you will be hated by all nations for my

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:18.710
name's sake. And then many will be

00:07:18.720 --> 00:07:21.270
offended and repelled and will begin to

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:23.350
distrust and desert him whom they ought

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:25.749
to trust and obey and will stumble and

00:07:25.759 --> 00:07:27.670
fall away and betray one another and

00:07:27.680 --> 00:07:30.309
pursue one another with hatred. And many

00:07:30.319 --> 00:07:32.390
false prophets will rise up and deceive

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:34.950
and lead many into error. And the love

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:37.189
of the great body of people will grow

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:39.670
cold because of the multiplied

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:43.309
lawlessness and iniquity.'Okay, pause.

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:46.230
So, He's warning right there that

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:48.790
there's going to be a lot of people fall

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:52.350
away. There's going to be a lot of

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:55.430
people that are going to be persecuted

00:07:55.440 --> 00:07:57.909
for His name's sake.

00:07:59.120 --> 00:08:01.749
You're going to be tested basically by

00:08:01.759 --> 00:08:03.830
the world persecuting you because you're

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:06.710
a Christian. Then He said we're going to

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:11.749
see lots of false prophets rise up.

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:13.749
I don't know—like I've said this

00:08:13.749 --> 00:08:13.759
before—I

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:15.909
don't know of any other denomination

00:08:15.919 --> 00:08:18.150
or belief system that has prophets

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:19.990
other than the Christian

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.430
community. We don't have Buddhist

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:23.029
prophets. We don't have Muhammad

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:25.110
prophets.

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:27.350
I haven't heard any, but there's a lot of

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:29.189
Christians and a lot of it is the

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:33.110
charismatic circle. Many false prophets

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:34.870
are going to rise up. So does that make

00:08:34.880 --> 00:08:37.829
these people bad? No. It just means

00:08:37.839 --> 00:08:39.990
they're not hearing Him. They're

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:42.149
down with the chickens. They're

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:44.230
not hearing a clear direction. So

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:48.150
anybody who gives a word that is off,

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:50.150
that automatically makes

00:08:50.150 --> 00:08:50.160
it

00:08:50.160 --> 00:08:52.470
false. But does that make them a bad

00:08:52.480 --> 00:08:55.190
person? No. Are they doing it out of

00:08:55.190 --> 00:08:55.200
malice?

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:58.550
Are they trying

00:08:58.560 --> 00:09:00.070
to be mean? Are they saying, 'Well, we're going

00:09:00.080 --> 00:09:02.550
to lead all these people astray'? No, I

00:09:02.560 --> 00:09:05.269
believe they're just missing it. Many

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:07.829
false prophets. It's not somebody that's

00:09:07.839 --> 00:09:09.190
out there. I don't believe there's a lot

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.630
of these people, because I've talked to

00:09:10.640 --> 00:09:14.230
them, that are doing it and trying to

00:09:14.240 --> 00:09:16.389
be deceitful.

00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:18.670
They're just down with the

00:09:18.680 --> 00:09:21.430
chickens and they're listening

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:23.910
in front of their face instead of

00:09:23.920 --> 00:09:26.470
coming up higher with the fire, getting

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:29.470
at the throne room and sitting at his

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:32.710
feet. You're going to see a

00:09:32.710 --> 00:09:32.720
bird's-eye

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:35.990
view, not a chicken-eye view down

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:39.910
here. So many false prophets. So,

00:09:39.920 --> 00:09:43.430
are we in the last days?

00:09:43.440 --> 00:09:46.470
I believe we are. So, what are we

00:09:46.480 --> 00:09:48.710
supposed to expect? We're supposed to

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:51.509
expect the things that he said in his

00:09:51.519 --> 00:09:54.150
word we would see. And this is the

00:09:54.160 --> 00:09:56.630
beginning of sorrows. And the Lord

00:09:56.640 --> 00:09:58.550
warned us this was coming. He said it

00:09:58.560 --> 00:09:59.910
would be the beginning of sorrows. That

00:09:59.920 --> 00:10:01.670
means we just started. So, if this is

00:10:01.680 --> 00:10:03.430
the beginning of sorrows, are there good

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:05.550
days

00:10:05.560 --> 00:10:07.990
ahead? I don't know. I mean, because the

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.670
word just said this is the beginning of

00:10:09.680 --> 00:10:12.470
sorrows. What does it mean to sorrow?

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.829
Sorrow doesn't sound like a good thing

00:10:13.839 --> 00:10:15.590
to me. I'm just saying that

00:10:15.590 --> 00:10:15.600
doesn't

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:17.910
sound like goosebumps and

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:20.310
everything. When I hear sorrows,

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:22.310
that seems sad. Sorrows is sad.

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:24.870
That's a sad time. So it's the beginning

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:27.829
of sorrows. So we have a lot of words

00:10:27.839 --> 00:10:29.750
being given, and I'm not

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:32.310
here to point out people,

00:10:32.320 --> 00:10:34.470
but we have a lot of words being given

00:10:34.480 --> 00:10:36.870
about the United States is going to do all

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:38.310
this stuff, and we're going to do all

00:10:38.320 --> 00:10:40.949
these things, and everything's going to

00:10:40.959 --> 00:10:43.590
get better for a season.

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:45.590
And the Lord told me

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:49.310
we have a window,

00:10:49.310 --> 00:10:49.320
a

00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:51.150
season of

00:10:51.160 --> 00:10:55.190
blessing for the remnant to get up the

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:57.630
wealth of the wicked to lay up for the

00:10:57.640 --> 00:11:00.630
righteous. He said,

00:11:00.630 --> 00:11:00.640
'Why?'Because

00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:04.110
there's great days of turbulence

00:11:04.120 --> 00:11:08.350
coming. Very hard days are

00:11:08.360 --> 00:11:11.590
coming. Matthew 24. So, let's

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:13.829
keep reading. 'But he who endures

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:16.230
to the end will be saved, and this good

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:18.150
news of the kingdom, the gospel, will be

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:19.829
preached throughout the whole world as a

00:11:19.839 --> 00:11:21.670
testimony to all the nations. And then

00:11:21.680 --> 00:11:23.829
will come the end.'So, we're going to

00:11:23.839 --> 00:11:25.990
see the gospel preached throughout the

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:28.550
whole world. And I'm telling you, I

00:11:28.560 --> 00:11:32.230
believe Starlink will have a big hand

00:11:32.240 --> 00:11:35.190
in this. Starlink, the internet,

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:37.190
bringing these satellites that the

00:11:37.200 --> 00:11:38.710
internet is preached throughout all the

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:40.710
devices, YouTube, and things like

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:44.550
that. The word is going forth

00:11:44.560 --> 00:11:47.750
into all nations. And it's not by

00:11:47.760 --> 00:11:49.910
internet cable anymore. It's by a link.

00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:51.509
You can have it on your phone and

00:11:51.519 --> 00:11:53.269
you have a signal, and all of a sudden

00:11:53.279 --> 00:11:55.190
you're able to see the word anywhere in

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:58.310
the world by a signal. So it will be

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:01.110
preached throughout the whole world and

00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:03.350
